data.description: Charming 3 BR 2 FB ranch style home with a basement on a .75 acre lot with a fenced in back yard. NO HOA! This home features a split floor plan, vaulted ceilings and a large primary bedroom w/walk-in closet.  New LVP flooring, carpet, and paint in 2022. New fixtures throughout main living area. Kitchen features new SS appliances with gas range, refrigerator conveys. Back deck off the kitchen is perfect for grilling. Basement is partially finished with an opportunity to add more heated living area in the future! It is plumbed for a full bath, has a laundry room with a sink and the washer and dryer conveys.  Great potential for a future bonus/recreation room, or lots of storage. There is a 320 sq ft storage building/workshop w/electric in the back yard.  New Septic tank in 2022. One car garage with plenty of parking. Great location!  Minutes from I-77, LKN State Park, Downtown Troutman, Devast'e Vineyard's, and Zootastic.
